{
  "stem": "17625.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 172.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was the [NON-ENGLISH], Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- I-- I was in the army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they called [NON-ENGLISH] which is heavy-- heavy equipped machine guns.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Polish, it's-- [NON-ENGLISH] is the word for heavy machine guns.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there-- there I was till-- till September.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How to use it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, it was-- it was-- it was distributed in in certain ways.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One was carrying ammunition.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One was carrying the gun.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The gun was from two parts, one which-- which you put up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The other one was the real thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [SIGHS] sometimes, I was-- I-- I was given given the-- the-- the stand, which was the heaviest.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] That's what it was-- not always.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How were you--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Otherwise, you have to carry two-- two boxes of-- of-- of ammunition to-- to-- to the-- to the position.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sometimes I had a good corporal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And sometimes I had a dog.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Which means, in in in Jewish-- you know what I mean-- anti-Semite.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- but overall, I held out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Called me names.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, it was anti-Semitism, a lot of anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- but overall, I held up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I held up to that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But-- but-- but I didn't even-- I wasn't even long there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because the war broke out in-- in September.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was from-- from March to September.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We haven't finished yet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because my father didn't go for it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he-- he had a doctor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had a middleman which had connections to a doctor, a military doctor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] something-- they thought of something to pull me out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They gave me some-- some things to take.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and-- and the blood test should show that's something there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it didn't work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It didn't work.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
